short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tab Counter, counts the number of opened tabs and windows

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Ultimate Tab counter helps you keep an eye on your opened tabs count, Opened windows count and opened Incognito windows count. Opened tabs across all windows can be seen with the batch on extension icon.

To track incognito windows and tab count, please enable Allow in Incognito for Ultimate Tab Counter extension, open chrome://extensions/ in Google Chrome

We don't collect or share information to any 3rd parties Keep on updating for new features. For suggestions, write us on fireicetechltd(@)gmail(.)com
